Utterance.UttText: Hercules kokkinakis, 76 yrs old under Dr Kenzie came in found by wife on the floor unconscious and not breathing.
He's got history on diabetes type 2, sleep apnoea, and he is overweight.
He is stable but he is still on ventilator.
He is to start physio next shift.
. He will be discharged to intensive care as soon as there will be room or if he gets worse.
